{"tid":223040,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫有貓家庭少於兩隻，做太耐貓義工係咪會降低智商","createTime":"2017-04-30T04:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T07:51:23.000Z","uid":30807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa447352c4ecb9465ad41d963a845471f0463187","tid":223040,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/123637_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F123637_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=69449914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔理你隻隻字打做只字啦<br />\n<br />\n有貓家庭少於兩隻係咩事，一定要有貓但一定要少於兩隻？點解唔直接講你屋企一定要有一隻貓？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nok佢句野可能係指如果你本身有貓，你最多只能有一隻貓，但係都冇撚理由<br />\n<br />\n隻貓都一歲半，親唔親貓已經固定左<br />\n<br />\n如果唔親，根本唔應該比本身有貓既人養<br />\n<br />\n如果親，你唔比我屋企夠大養三隻？<br />\n<br />\n同埋我最撚嬲係25歲規定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大左一定會錫貓？ 驚人太窮養唔起咪直接講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1623e90b4ed04d21b4f6c315255b3c0f28bb541","tid":223040,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"25歲以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家生仔咩<br />\n25歲有d人連仔都有啦"},{"pid":"61eafa343534b23c31dee950551affd8fc09984a","tid":223040,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:14:12.000Z","msg":"求人地收養仲要咁多要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ba043a1cac368b4b8864e7ffb043a02276c617","tid":223040,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"呢 d 多數都係 template 黎"},{"pid":"79821942fda0ce570105410ba816a99a561d979f","tid":223040,"uid":102956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:51:23.000Z","msg":"好似D on9仔想扮用日文個種文風去寫野咁<img src=\"/as